## Installation

```lua
loadstring(game:HttpGet("https://raw.githubusercontent.com/10cxm/millenium-fixed/main/scr"))()
```

---

## Basic Setup

```lua
local window = library:window({
    name = "MyScript",
    suffix = "Hub",
    gameInfo = "Game Name Here",
    size = UDim2.new(0, 700, 0, 565)
})
```

### Window Properties
| Property | Type | Default | Description |
|----------|------|---------|-------------|
| name | string | "nebula" | Main title text |
| suffix | string | "tech" | Text after title |
| gameInfo | string | "Milenium for Counter-Strike: Global Offensive" | Bottom info text |
| size | UDim2 | UDim2.new(0, 700, 0, 565) | Window size |

### Window Methods
```lua
window.toggle_menu(bool)
window.minimize_menu(bool)
window.toggle_minimize()
library:unload_menu()
```

**Methods:**
- `toggle_menu(bool)` - Show/hide entire UI
- `minimize_menu(bool)` - Minimize to title bar only (true) or restore (false)
- `toggle_minimize()` - Toggle between minimized and full size
- `unload_menu()` - Completely destroy and cleanup UI

---

## Tabs

```lua
local tab1, tab2, tab3 = window:tab({
    name = "Combat",
    icon = "rbxassetid://6034767608",
    tabs = {"Section1", "Section2", "Section3"}
})
```

### Tab Properties
| Property | Type | Default | Description |
|----------|------|---------|-------------|
| name | string | "visuals" | Tab name |
| icon | string | "rbxassetid://6034767608" | Tab icon |
| tabs | table | {"Main", "Misc.", "Settings"} | Sub-sections |

### Returns
Returns multiple tab objects (one for each sub-section defined in `tabs`)

---

## Layout

### Column
```lua
local column = tab:column({
    size = 0.5
})
```

| Property | Type | Default | Description |
|----------|------|---------|-------------|
| size | number | 1 | Column width (0-1) |

### Sub Tab
```lua
local subTab = tab:sub_tab({
    order = 0,
    size = 1
})
```

| Property | Type | Default | Description |
|----------|------|---------|-------------|
| order | number | 0 | Layout order |
| size | number | 1 | Sub-tab size |

### Section
```lua
local section = column:section({
    name = "Section Name",
    size = 1,
    icon = "rbxassetid://6022668898",
    fading = false
})
```

| Property | Type | Default | Description |
|----------|------|---------|-------------|
| name | string | "section" | Section title |
| size | number | 0.5 | Section height (0-1) |
| icon | string | "rbxassetid://6022668898" | Section icon |
| fading | boolean | false | Enable collapsible toggle |

---

## Elements

### Toggle

#### Checkbox Style
```lua
section:toggle({
    name = "Enable Feature",
    default = false,
    type = "checkbox",
    callback = function(value) end,
    flag = "my_toggle",
    info = "Additional info text",
    seperator = true
})
```

#### Toggle Style
```lua
section:toggle({
    name = "Enable Feature",
    default = false,
    type = "toggle",
    callback = function(value) end
})
```

| Property | Type | Default | Description |
|----------|------|---------|-------------|
| name | string | "Toggle" | Toggle name |
| default | boolean | false | Initial state |
| type | string | random | "checkbox" or "toggle" |
| callback | function | empty | Called on change |
| flag | string | auto | Config flag name |
| info | string | nil | Info text below toggle |
| seperator | boolean | false | Show separator below |

### Slider

```lua
section:slider({
    name = "Value",
    min = 0,
    max = 100,
    default = 50,
    interval = 1,
    suffix = "%",
    callback = function(value) end,
    flag = "my_slider",
    info = "Slider info text",
    seperator = true
})
```

| Property | Type | Default | Description |
|----------|------|---------|-------------|
| name | string | nil | Slider name |
| min | number | 0 | Minimum value |
| max | number | 100 | Maximum value |
| default | number | 10 | Initial value |
| interval | number | 1 | Step size |
| suffix | string | "" | Text after value |
| callback | function | empty | Called on change |
| flag | string | auto | Config flag name |
| info | string | nil | Info text |
| seperator | boolean | true | Show separator |

### Dropdown

#### Single Select
```lua
section:dropdown({
    name = "Option",
    items = {"Option1", "Option2", "Option3"},
    default = "Option1",
    multi = false,
    callback = function(value) end,
    flag = "my_dropdown",
    width = 130,
    info = "Dropdown info",
    seperator = true
})
```

#### Multi Select
```lua
section:dropdown({
    name = "Options",
    items = {"Option1", "Option2", "Option3"},
    default = {"Option1"},
    multi = true,
    callback = function(values) end
})
```

| Property | Type | Default | Description |
|----------|------|---------|-------------|
| name | string | nil | Dropdown name |
| items | table | {""} | Available options |
| default | string/table | first item | Initial selection |
| multi | boolean | false | Multi-select mode |
| callback | function | empty | Called on change |
| flag | string | auto | Config flag name |
| width | number | 130 | Dropdown width |
| info | string | nil | Info text |
| seperator | boolean | true | Show separator |

### Methods
```lua
dropdown.set(value)
dropdown.refresh_options(newItems)
dropdown.set_visible(bool)
```

### Keybind

```lua
section:keybind({
    name = "Keybind",
    key = Enum.KeyCode.E,
    mode = "Toggle",
    default = false,
    callback = function(active) end,
    flag = "my_keybind"
})
```

| Property | Type | Default | Description |
|----------|------|---------|-------------|
| name | string | nil | Keybind name |
| key | KeyCode | nil | Initial key |
| mode | string | "Toggle" | "Toggle", "Hold", or "Always" |
| default | boolean | false | Initial active state |
| callback | function | empty | Called on state change |
| flag | string | auto | Config flag name |

### Methods
```lua
keybind.set(input)
keybind.set_mode(mode)
keybind.set_visible(bool)
```

### Colorpicker

```lua
section:colorpicker({
    name = "Color",
    color = Color3.fromRGB(255, 255, 255),
    alpha = 0.5,
    callback = function(color, alpha) end,
    flag = "my_color",
    seperator = false
})
```

| Property | Type | Default | Description |
|----------|------|---------|-------------|
| name | string | "Color" | Colorpicker name |
| color | Color3 | Color3.new(1,1,1) | Initial color |
| alpha | number | 0 | Initial transparency (0-1) |
| callback | function | empty | Called on change |
| flag | string | auto | Config flag name |
| seperator | boolean | false | Show separator |

### Methods
```lua
colorpicker.set(color, alpha)
colorpicker.set_visible(bool)
```

### Textbox

```lua
section:textbox({
    name = "Text Input",
    placeholder = "Type here...",
    default = "",
    callback = function(text) end,
    flag = "my_textbox"
})
```

| Property | Type | Default | Description |
|----------|------|---------|-------------|
| name | string | "TextBox" | Textbox label |
| placeholder | string | "type here..." | Placeholder text |
| default | string | "" | Initial text |
| callback | function | empty | Called on change |
| flag | string | auto | Config flag name |

### Methods
```lua
textbox.set(text)
```

### Button

```lua
section:button({
    name = "Click Me",
    callback = function() end
})
```

| Property | Type | Default | Description |
|----------|------|---------|-------------|
| name | string | "TextBox" | Button text |
| callback | function | empty | Called on click |

### Label

```lua
section:label({
    name = "Label Text",
    info = "Additional info",
    seperator = false
})
```

| Property | Type | Default | Description |
|----------|------|---------|-------------|
| name | string | "Toggle" | Label text |
| info | string | nil | Additional info |
| seperator | boolean | false | Show separator |

### List

```lua
section:list({
    options = {"Item1", "Item2", "Item3"},
    flag = "my_list",
    callback = function(selected) end
})
```

| Property | Type | Default | Description |
|----------|------|---------|-------------|
| options | table | {"1","2","3"} | List items |
| flag | string | auto | Config flag name |
| callback | function | empty | Called on selection |

### Methods
```lua
list.refresh_options(newOptions)
```

---

## Notifications

```lua
library.notifications:create_notification({
    name = "Title",
    info = "Description text here",
    lifetime = 3
})
```

| Property | Type | Default | Description |
|----------|------|---------|-------------|
| name | string | "This is a title!" | Notification title |
| info | string | "This is extra info!" | Notification text |
| lifetime | number | 3 | Duration in seconds |

---

## Configuration

### Save Config
```lua
local config = library:get_config()
writefile(library.directory .. "/configs/myconfig.cfg", config)
```

### Load Config
```lua
local config = readfile(library.directory .. "/configs/myconfig.cfg")
library:load_config(config)
```

### Delete Config
```lua
delfile(library.directory .. "/configs/myconfig.cfg")
```

### Update Config List
```lua
library:update_config_list()
```

### Accessing Flags
```lua
library.flags["my_toggle"]
library.flags["my_slider"]
library.flags["my_dropdown"]
```

---

## Theming

### Change Accent Color
```lua
library:update_theme("accent", Color3.fromRGB(255, 100, 150))
```

### Set Theme on Load
```lua
loadstring(game:HttpGet("https://raw.githubusercontent.com/10cxm/millenium-fixed/main/scr"))()
library:update_theme("accent", Color3.fromRGB(100, 200, 255))
```

---

## Utility Functions

### Tweening
```lua
library:tween(object, {Property = value}, EasingStyle, time)
```

### Draggify
```lua
library:draggify(frame)
```

### Resizify
```lua
library:resizify(frame)
```

### Create Instance
```lua
library:create("Frame", {
    Parent = parent,
    Size = UDim2.new(1, 0, 1, 0)
})
```

### Connections
```lua
local connection = library:connection(signal, function() end)
```

### Next Flag
```lua
local flag = library:next_flag()
```

